summary: Clark Gregg Says 'Captain Marvel' May be the Famous 'Rodeo'
title: Clark Gregg Says 'Captain Marvel' May be the Famous 'Rodeo'
body:
Clark Gregg Says #CaptainMarvel May be the Famous ‘Rodeo’

Marvel Cinematic Universe fans remember when we first met Phil Coulson, he told Tony Stark that the Iron Man incident wasn’t his first rodeo. Fans have speculated that since Coulson is involved in the events of the 90s-set Captain Marvel that we’d finally see his first rodeo.

In an interview with Entertainment Weekly, Clark Gregg confirms the movie may be that rodeo:

“This might be the rodeo,”…

summary: Marvel Shares New Images from Captain Marvel We get another look at Brie Larson all suited up as Captain Marvel / Carol Danvers....
caption:
Marvel Shares New Images from Captain Marvel

We get another look at Brie Larson all suited up as Captain Marvel / Carol Danvers.

And here we are on Hala, the Kree planet, with Starforce. Led by Jude Law’s character, his team is comprised of Ronan (Lee Pace), Korath (Djimon Hounsou), Att-Lass (Algenis Perez Soto), Captain Marvel (Brie Larson), Bron-Char (Rune Temte) and Minn-Erva (Gemma Chan).

And here we have Ben Mendelsohn and his “misunderstood” Skrulls.

For these and more images head on over to Marvel.

Captain Marvel, directed by Anna Boden and Ryan Fleck, hits theaters March 8, 2019.

summary: Captain Marvel's Budget Appears to Be $152 Million
title: Captain Marvel's Budget Appears to Be $152 Million
body:
Marvel Studios is known for being very economical with the budgets on their solo movies. That’s one of the reasons why the deal with Sony was made, as Spider-Man: Homecoming cost a lot less to make than The Amazing Spider-Man 2 and ended up making more money as well. And now we may know how much Captain Marvel cost to make.

A filing on the Louisiana Office of Entertainment Industry Developmentrev…

summary: War Machine Story Did I mention I'm an MCU fanboy now? Never read the comics, but I know that Carol and Rhodey were a couple at...
caption:
War Machine Story

Did I mention I’m an MCU fanboy now?

Never read the comics, but I know that Carol and Rhodey were a couple at some point. I doubt they’ll hook up in the MCU ‘cause of the whole age difference thing, but I think a mentor/student relationship between them would be pretty cute.

blog.title: Bring back Genis and Phyla Vell
blog.description:
Site dedicated to all things Genis-Vell and Phyla-Vell. Former Captains Marvel and son and daughter of the original one, Mar-Vell. They were killed off very soon by Marvel and they deserve a second chance, we don't ask about a new chance as Captains Marvel but to come back to the Cosmic Marvel Universe (Quasar, Photon, Legacy, Martyr, whatever). 

Posts about Genis and Phyla. Mar-Vell, Rick Jones, Guardians of the Galaxy, Adam Warlock, Quasar, Thanos, Starlin stuff, some Avengers and a lot of Cosmic stuff. Welcome!
